{"tid":1594373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［各位巴絲幫幫手］點樣喺官中表達訴求？","createTime":"2019-09-25T13:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T14:06:37.000Z","uid":204133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f6067077a83912fcfeb3593b86c284b58265046f","tid":1594373,"uid":204133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T13:59:36.000Z","msg":"［幫朋友代po］<br />\n<br />\n我係荃官人，我哋有壁報設計比賽，有好幾班都打算整連儂牆，結果驚動校方，甚至係校董。垃圾校長、校董同埋校工上課室撕文宣。<br />\n撕一貼百，佢哋係咁撕，我哋係咁黐。但係咁樣並唔係長久之計，各位巴絲有咩計？"},{"pid":"7bddb838052da897d074234882cdc96b1e151676","tid":1594373,"uid":204133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:01:19.000Z","msg":"自推10連1/10"},{"pid":"7f0477ca59e5307793815eac5d99d5354b31fdc4","tid":1594373,"uid":204133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:01:39.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"ece873b93cf436c6e1c77d56995ed3796d180e93","tid":1594373,"uid":204133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"4f7d4df6fc8264a9caa21ee6e97eec0e17a4208f","tid":1594373,"uid":204133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:02:08.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"bbb1324a422faa2a5ce023a754a9a3ad993a1ee9","tid":1594373,"uid":204133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"e8a957939fbeef5cdb51c3fd51814c229a8ec942","tid":1594373,"uid":204133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:02:31.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"c692d29ad9d78cd656d4b48b8063cc263095092b","tid":1594373,"uid":300424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:02:33.000Z","msg":"照做可也！"},{"pid":"aa14a82ebe21432a3391bdca0c4b1faa77886742","tid":1594373,"uid":204133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:02:41.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"936d317849d3e8d4b66ae9d5255718d79264145f","tid":1594373,"uid":204133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0